  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Researcher Link Workshop Grant April 2018-19</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Grants for workshops in priority research areas defined at a country level, which allow UK and Indian  researchers to share their research and establish long term and sustainable links. Workshops are intended to support research areas relevant to the economic development and welfare of partner countries.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">To build sustainable research links between the UK and India and build capacity for engagement in international research collaboration in areas that are identified. Workshops are intended to support research areas relevant to the economic development and welfare of partner countries.</narrative>
  </description>
